reviewText: Fun and cute. Light hearted comedy. I laughed out loud through out.

I bought this because of the male lead.  He is the highest paid singer in the world, grew up in America, he's even got a Masters degree in music.  Well any-ways I liked him in the movie he made with Charlie Chan called "Little Big Solider" and my daughters thought he was handsome too...  This movie is a light weight comedy and can be enjoyed for just that...light comedy.
